mozda zauvek...

25
00:03:16,484 --> 00:03:19,419
...dok ja imam moje cetiri
devojke da me utese.

26
00:03:19,554 --> 00:03:22,522
I one su prava uteha,
zar ne?

27
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:25,522
